<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Heideck, Viztum in Bayern, Heinrich und Hans von Absberg und Schweicker von Gundelfingen</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Entsendung von Hans Stetzmann und Marquart Waltmann, Diener der Stadt, wegen der Fehdeerklärung des Hiltpolt von Fraunberg zu Herzog Stephan III. von Bayern-Ingolstadt mit und bittet um Unterstützung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_184" id="90v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_184_r2l1">Johanſen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Heẏdeck / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r2l2"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>rcʒog</expan> Stephans vicʒtum in Bayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_184_r2l3">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir ſenden cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> Stephans 
<del rend="strikethrough"> gnaden </del> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r2l4">Hanſen Steͣcʒman vnd <expan>Markart<ex>en</ex></expan> Waltman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> diener / mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r2l5">ſeinen gnaden cʒu reden von ſölchs entſagens wegen / als vns her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r2l6">hıltpolt <expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd etliche dıe ſeinen getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r2l7"> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_184_line_1571062584232_916">den </ab></add> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough">n</del></expan> diener 
<del rend="strikethrough"> n </del> darŷnne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_184_r2l8">gen 
