</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_184" id="90v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Johansen, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Heydeck,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>rczog</expan> Stephans,
                        vicztum in Bayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden czu
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan> Stephans,
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> Hansen Steͣczman und
                                <expan>Markart<ex>en</ex></expan> Waltman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> diener, mit seinen gnaden czu reden von
                        sölchs entsagens wegen, als uns her Hiltpolt
                            <expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> und etliche die seinen getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, daz ir <add>den</add>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener,
                        darynne gen <add><expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan> Stephan,
                                <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und behoffen sein wöllet, daz
                        sie darümb von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gnediklich auszgeriht und gevertigt
                                <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen und <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Absperg, geprudern, <lb/>Sweigker von <expan>Gundelfinge<ex>n</ex></expan> dem
                        jungen <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
